===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Valerie (Masters)}}
Valerie forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Sylveon}} and {{p|Mawile}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Valerie joins the {{player}} after completing the twenty-third chapter of the [[PML arc]]. 

Valerie has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, the PML arc and [[Legendary Adventures]].

